Welcome to Wakie!
We're excited to see you using Wakie and our other products and services, all of which we refer to simply as the "Services." When we refer to Wakie, we mean Wakie, Wakie X, Wakie.com and our other products.
These Terms of Service (which we call the "Terms") govern our relationship with you. Although we have tried our best to strip the legalese from the Terms, there are places where these Terms may still read like a traditional contract. There's a good reason for that: These Terms do indeed form a legally binding contract between you and Wakie Inc. So please read them carefully.
By using the Services, you agree to the Terms. Of course, if you don't agree with them, then don't use the Services.
