Age Verification: Users must be at least 13 years old to create an account or use our Services. We implement measures to verify user ages and prevent underage access. Providing false information to circumvent age restrictions is a violation of our Terms.
Reporting Mechanism: We provide tools for users to report any content or behavior suspected of involving CSAE. Reports are confidential and reviewed promptly. Users are encouraged to report any violations immediately.
Cooperation with Authorities: Wakie Inc. cooperates fully with law enforcement agencies in investigating and prosecuting CSAE offenses. We may report suspected CSAE content or activity to relevant authorities as required by law.
Account Termination: Any user found engaging in CSAE activities will have their account terminated immediately and may be reported to law enforcement.
Parental Controls: We recommend that parents and guardians monitor their children's online activities. Resources such as
